eplyTime":"2017-11-20T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好記得當年班打手好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話咩用晒屋企所有設備全日開住hktv幫wiki巴打增加收視率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔睇既就係5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地仲話王維基係一個好老闆, 好想幫佢打工<br />\n<br />\n點知後來王維基 搞送貨.......<br />\n跟住D 員工因為待遇太差而罷工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n維基都算係好老闆<br />\n只係高層閪 又廢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我無記錯, 當時D 送貨佬罷工<br />\n<br />\n係因為維基用人唯親, 用自己既親信, 但D親信又西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無source?<br />\n果時好多低層員工讚維基喎<br />\ngoogle都有<br />\n仲有佢公開話開唔到台被逼栽員，但一定會優先請返佢地 ，雖然係空頭支票，但香港地有邊個老細會咁講野</blockquote><br />\n個倉垃圾到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個倉都搞唔掂<br />\n搞乜電視台</blockquote><br />\n個倉轉左自動化/轉緊啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我親戚做HKTV<br />\n之前開唔到台 幫佢係HKBN 搵埋工<br />\n開 HKTV MALL 個陣,又請返佢"},{"pid":"1eb451963d4ce4adbde73ad5e07db81f66bebd57","tid":473853,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"笑你老母咩<br />\n<br />\n唔公平情況下有撚得比"},{"pid":"ed5da2f1de5d46020dcac0612aa4807ae6740146","tid":473853,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ff8acc48e56d34117918196ae197b9133d4a95d","tid":473853,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd63d2be0cd5c8a93c0ce4fce2b60da16800b8f","tid":473853,"uid":74372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><bl